5 (11) Complete a value engineering study with respect to the Silver Line East as a
6 light rail line. For purposes of this section, "Silver Line East" means a mass
7 transit project that includes, at a minimum, service from the center of the City
8 of Charlotte through the Town of Matthews to the Levine Campus of Central
9 Piedmont Community College. The study shall include efforts to identify and,
10 if possible, procure the funding needed to establish the Silver Line East as a
