21 supplies, materials, or equipment is the most appropriate acquisition method prior to the issuance
22 of the requests for proposals and shall by formal motion certify that the requirements of this
23 subsection have been followed before approving the contract.
24 Nothing in this subsection subjects a procurement by competitive proposal under this
25 subsection to G.S. 143-49, 143-52, or 143-53.
