48 PART IX. STATE FUNDING PROVISIONS
49 SECTION 9.1. It is the intent of the General Assembly not to reduce transportation
50 funding allocations for any municipality in Mecklenburg County as a result of the enactment of
51 this act or the levy of a tax under the provisions of this act. In addition, it is the intent of the
Page 26 House Bill 948-Fourth Edition

